HEADWORD: Trust company
<hw>Trust company</hw>. <def>Any corporation formed for the purpose of
acting as trustee. Such companies usually do more or less of a banking
business.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

